readable.content: A black dog is running along the beach beside a brown dog in midair catching a stick in its mouth . A black dog runs on the shore while a light brown dog jumps up to catch a stick . A brown dog leaps into the air next to a black dog on a sandy bay . On a beach , black and brown dog runs , brown dog jumps . Two dogs are playing together
